H0.text: Senses are the second part of the central nervous system, which consists of the brain and the senses.

H1.text: Organs are the second part of the central nervous system, the other part being the brain.

H2.text: Muscles are the second part of the central nervous system, which consists of the brain and the muscles.

H3.text: Spinal cord is the second part of the central nervous system, which also includes the brain.

A4.text: Together, the brain and spinal cord make up the central nervous system.
